Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.72,Main,Shi,0,0,0,,Kluci už na nás čekají, Mami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:04.40,Main,Shi,0,0,0,,Oh, píšeš kamarádovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.43,Main,M,0,0,0,,Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:10.54,Main,M,0,0,0,,Už se nemůžu dočkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:14.00,Main,M,0,0,0,,Chci říct, jsme u moře, pojďme si to užít!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.96,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\b1\bord2.25\3c&H555655&\4c&H4C4D41&\shad6.75\fs67.5\c&HF1E8DA&\fsp9\frx18\fry16\fax.1\frz352.9\pos(747.925,625.334)}Stanice Izukyu-Shimoda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.42,Main,Kawanaka,0,0,0,,Whoa, krásná Cesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.76,Main,Shinbo,0,0,0,,Já si dám Shimoda Burger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.96,Main,Kawa,0,0,0,,Pospěš si, Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... Už jdu.
