Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.04,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(1435.472,450,-350.943,450)\fnArial\b1\fs90\c&HFBFFB3&\3c&HAD6334&\shad0\an1}Buď klidný
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.08,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(1435.472,450,-350.943,450)\fnArial\b1\fs90\c&HFBFFB3&\3c&HAD6334&\shad0\an1}Buď klidný
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.22,Italics,K,0,0,0,,Ne, když se nepodívám,\N budu toho navždy litovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.22,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(1435.472,450,224.151,450)\fnArial\b1\fs90\c&HFBFFB3&\3c&HAD6334&\shad0\an1}Buď klidný
