Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jsi tam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.03,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H9A5555&\bord0\shad0\an5\frz281.8\pos(783.396,270)\b1}Co teď?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.82,Main,C,0,0,0,,Běž! Nemáme žádnou jinou možnost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:55.41,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H9A5555&\bord0\shad0\an5\b1\frz263\pos(1331.321,364.5)}Co teď?
